==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Parle
<hw>Parle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>parler</ets>. See <er>Parley</er>.]</ety> <def>To talk; to
converse; to parley.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Finding himself too weak, began to <qex>parle</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Parle</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Parle
<hw>Parle</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Conversation; talk; parley.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They ended <qex>parle</qex>, and both addressed for fight.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Parley</ent>⟦br⟧
